1
00:00:02,166 --> 00:00:03,166
So where...

2
00:00:03,266 --> 00:00:05,833
is the guy that we ask him to guide us?

3
00:00:06,300 --> 00:00:07,766
The guy's name Phupha.

4
00:00:08,133 --> 00:00:09,133
He's not here yet.

5
00:00:09,833 --> 00:00:10,266
Right?

6
00:00:10,833 --> 00:00:11,666
It's quite awhile now.

7
00:00:11,666 --> 00:00:12,666
It's noon already.

8
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:14,099
He said he's almost here.

9
00:00:18,066 --> 00:00:19,066
So damn hot.

10
00:00:24,133 --> 00:00:25,413
Does he know how to drive a car?

11
00:00:25,533 --> 00:00:26,533
Is this your guide?

12
00:00:26,733 --> 00:00:27,733
Probably.

13
00:00:34,666 --> 00:00:35,199
Hello, everyone.

14
00:00:35,566 --> 00:00:36,566
- Hello, bro.
- Hi.

15
00:00:36,900 --> 00:00:37,966
You are Phupha, right?

16
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:40,460
I just delivered Master Boon some food.

17
00:00:40,533 --> 00:00:41,533
Sorry for the late.

18
00:00:43,500 --> 00:00:44,500
Come on, P'Phu.

19
00:00:44,533 --> 00:00:46,733
You talk like delivered
your boyfriend some food.

20
00:00:47,633 --> 00:00:48,933
Chill out a bit, bro.

21
00:00:49,566 --> 00:00:52,000
By the way, what about Master Boon, P' Phu?

22
00:00:52,500 --> 00:00:54,199
Does he know that...

23
00:00:54,633 --> 00:00:55,673
we are doing the research?

24
00:00:55,966 --> 00:00:57,133
I already told him.

25
00:00:57,500 --> 00:00:59,400
How about we get some rest first?

26
00:00:59,900 --> 00:01:01,342
Tomorrow, I'll get you guys to Master Boon.

27
00:01:01,366 --> 00:01:03,966
And if we got more free time,
I'll give you a tour in the village.

28
00:01:04,333 --> 00:01:05,333
Roger, bro.

29
00:01:05,433 --> 00:01:06,433
- That's good.
- Let's go.

30
00:01:06,599 --> 00:01:07,033
It's hot.

31
00:01:07,333 --> 00:01:08,333
Where do I sit?

32
00:01:08,500 --> 00:01:09,700
You guys take the pickup seat.

33
00:01:21,166 --> 00:01:22,166
It's still hot.
